snippet.title: Metal Gear Solid Delta: Snake Eater - Trailer | TGS 2024
snippet.description:
Check out the latest trailer for Metal Gear Solid Delta, the remake of MGS3: Snake Eater. This TGS trailer features brand new footage from the Virtuous Mission, including your first look at EVA.

#MetalGearSolid #MetalGear #Gaming
